{
  "texts": [
    "A Python library named contractions is used to expand the shortened words in sentences.",
    "For example, 'you're' is fixed to you 'are'.",
    "Expanding contractions are done to aid the recognition of grammatical categories in POS tagging.",
    "Part-of-speech (POS) tagging.",
    "POS taggers process a sequence of words and attach a part of a speech tag to each word."
  ]
}